int majorityElement(vector<int>& nums) {
    int n = nums.size();
    srand(unsigned(time(NULL)));
    while (true) {
        int idx = rand() % n;
        int candidate = nums[idx];
        int counts = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++)
            if (nums[i] == candidate)
                counts++;
        if (counts > n / 2) return candidate;
    }
}
```

* `Moore Voting Algorithm`:

```c++
int majorityElement(vector<int>& nums) {
    int major, counts = 0, n = nums.size();
    for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
        if (!counts) {
            major = nums[i];
            counts = 1;
        }
        else counts += (nums[i] == major) ? 1 : -1;
    }
    return major;
}
```

