[Maximum Length of Repeated Subarray](https://leetcode.com/problems/maximum-length-of-repeated-subarray/):

DPLCS

`dp[i, j]``A[i]``B[j]`

$$
dp[i, j] = \left\{
    \begin{aligned}
        0 &, & A[i] \neq B[i] \\
        dp[i-1, j-1] + 1 &, & A[i] = B[i]
    \end{aligned}
\right.
$$

`dp`

```c++
int findLength(vector<int>& A, vector<int>& B) {
    int n = A.size();
    if (n == 0) return 0;

    vector<int> dp(n+1, 0);
    int res = 0;
    for(int i = 1;i <= n; i++) {
        for(int j = n;j >= 1; j--) {
            dp[j] = (A[i-1] == B[j-1]) ? (dp[j-1] + 1) : 0;
            res = max(dp[j], res);
        }
    }

    return res;
}
```

