>     \       /     /      / \      \
>     3     2     1      1   3      2
>     /     /       \                 \
>     2     1         2                 3



`n=1` -> `1`
`n=2` -> `2`
`n=3` -> `5`

`n=3`,`1,2,3`,`1,2,3`

* `root=1``2,3``2,3``BST`,`BST``numsTrees(2)`.
* `root=2``1`,`3`.
* `root=3``1,2``numsTrees(2)`.

`n=5`

* `root=3``1,2`BST`4,5`BST`numsTree(5-3)*numsTrees(3-1)`



* `n < 2` -> `numsTrees(n) = 1`
* `n >= 2` -> `numsTrees(n) = numsTrees(1)*numsTrees(n-1) + numsTrees(2)*numTree(n-2) + ... + numsTree(n-1)*numsTrees(1)`;

:

```c++
int numTrees(int n) {
    if (n <= 1) return 1;

    int ret = 0;
    for(int i = 1;i <= n;i++) {
        int left = i-1;
        int right = n-i;
        ret += numTrees(left)*numTrees(right);
    }
    return ret;
}
