- `minutes * 720 / 60` or `minutes * 12`



```c++
double angleClock(int hour, int minutes) {
	hour = hour % 12;
	minutes = minutes % 60;
	hour = hour * 60 + minutes;
	minutes = minutes * 12;
	return min(720 - abs(hour - minutes), abs(hour - minutes)) / 2.0;
}
